<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-19-0798 </DOCNO><TEXT>This book presents papers on ballistic missile defense. Topics consideredinclude the historical aspects of US strategic concepts and programs,Soviet perspectives on the Strategic Defense Initiative (SDI), nationalsecurity, international cooperation, nuclear proliferation, arms controland SDI, the technical feasibility of the SDI, foreign policy, and USand Soviet views on prospects for a cooperative transition in strategicdefense.</TEXT></DOC>